findings.title: Initializer
findings.description: The initializer function can be called multiple times, potentially leading to unintended behavior.

findings.title: Unprotected public functions
findings.description: Multiple public functions are unprotected and can be accessed by anyone, potentially leading to unauthorized state changes or asset transfers.

findings.title: Unprotected external functions
findings.description: The functions includeInReward, setTaxFeePercent, setLiquidityFeePercent, and setMaxTxPercent are unprotected and can be called by anyone.
